{"id":19167,"title":"[Operation preparedness of specialized anti-epidemic brigades during mass events].","abstract":"Operation experience of specialized anti-epidemic brigades (SAEB) for the support of sanitary-epidemiologic welfare during various emergencies is presented. The order of functioning and SAEB objectives during mass events is examined. Analysis of exercise of Stavropol Institute of Plague Control SAEB was carried out, proposals for augmentation of SAEB equipment table by instruments and reagents for indication and genotyping of pathogen strains are examined.","date":"2014-04-17","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24738299","annotations":[{"name":"Pathogen","weight":0.50138,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pathogen"},{"name":"Plague (disease)","weight":0.15647,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plague_(disease)"},{"name":"Strain (biology)","weight":0.0532834,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strain_(biology)"},{"name":"Genotype","weight":0.0400013,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Genotype"},{"name":"Physical exercise","weight":0.0332387,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physical_exercise"},{"name":"Stavropol","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stavropol"},{"name":"Mass","weight":0.0227187,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mass"},{"name":"Instrument flight rules","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Instrument_flight_rules"},{"name":"Mathematical analysis","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_analysis"},{"name":"Order (biology)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Order_(biology)"},{"name":"Brigade","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brigade"},{"name":"Reagent","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikip